comment.narrative:
for Dutch Companies 5 direct business leads were identified and discussed with the peruvian delegationin the following fields:

1- Landfill gas extraction technologies; 
2- Landfill construction technologies (mineral lining systems and engineering, supervision) 
3- Waste to Energy by large scale incineration plants for Lima were discussed with Lima Mayor and the Peruvian private investment unit; 
4- Metal recycling technologies for Piura are now being studied in cooperation between Dutch company, 5- Piura Municipality and private local companies, institutional consultancy and legal advice for Piura was carried out directly after this project by Dutch and local consultants on a commercial basis)
